Quickstrike:




Quickstrike's optics went wide at Black Arachnia. She hadn't deleted 
it. He thought she would because of the danger, but she decided. He 
looked around. "Did ya get uh pod?" Oh, he hoped she did, then he 
would have no idea how to get their offspring on-line. If they could 
get the spark into the pod, it would be fine.

This whole thing made him nervous. It could harm her, and he didn't 
want that. If it started to, he'd destroy it. He didn't want to loose 
her because of it. It wasn't anything to him yet.

He grabbed her around the waist, just incase to steady her. Now he 
needed a place to take her. He picked her up in his arms. He heard a 
female lost a lot of energy from his type of procedure.

"Tell me what t' do," he said. What room would work in bringing it on-
line? 

He thought. Maybe he could get someone to help.
